    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/f8bb996163c8aff543fb4016b0760cd8.poster.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/f8bb996163c8aff543fb4016b0760cd8.webm?t=1696604379\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/f8bb996163c8aff543fb4016b0760cd8.mp4?t=1696604379\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>升级自己的角色，证明自己是位实打实的传送门骑士，创作出史诗级的武器，并在这部合作性3D沙盒动作RPG中征服敌人。<br><br>探索数十个随机生成的岛屿！建造几乎任何东西！在这个被地裂撕裂，被空洞王威胁的世界里，你和你的朋友是唯一的希望！<br><br><strong>打造你的冒险之旅。磨砺你的英雄气概。成为终极的传送门骑士！</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/4c5bdf215f23168115bcea3a326079c8.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><li>RPG 角色职业可供选择和控制。扮演战士、法师或猎人并自定义你的外观、技能和装备。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/8e1a9ad99c9ad9306ec3a03d1b038bee.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>使用几十种材料和陈设品建造你的家园。展示你在旅途中辛苦得到的珍宝。种植农场并在你的庄稼成熟时及时收割。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/7e4355b608331e996390c486a06482c5.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>策略动作战斗。在节奏紧张的第三人称视角战斗中攻击敌人并躲避他们的袭击。在各种各样的武器和法术中做出选择，击败敌人！<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/4a7e0ffb271f0635a03e45dd8f6af460.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>在随机生成的 3D 沙盒世界之间往来 — 每个世界都有独特的环境、生物和资源可用于制作。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/de5531123aebab6be6df48d62a1d0357.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>与你的好友一起体验 4 人合作游戏模式。齐心协力建造房屋、探索地下城并克服最艰难的险境。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/74055a9fa8e4e286221f17cce3380390.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>建造你的专属岛屿！在创意模式下快速轻松地创建令人惊叹的建筑！ <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/fb22244cba2690d5d1cf9f9ed68301ff.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>史诗级 BOSS 战。在这片土地上最可怕的野兽 - 传送门守卫的邪恶竞技场中与它们对峙。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/883b2e3aae1f498b2d7f3326608d048e.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>在各个地区采矿并搜集资源来堆砌你的军械库和物资。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/374040/extras/8c0be95aa6397b58fb5b16ed05177885.avif?t=1696604379\" width=600 height=200 /></span><br></li><li>随机事件</li></ul>",
